{"id":"api/router/testing","title":"@angular/router/testing","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router\", \"name\": \"@angular/router\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router/testing\", \"name\": \"@angular/router/testing\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/router\">@angular/router</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/router/testing/PACKAGE.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n<header class=\"api-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"angularroutertesting\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"et93bheqdur81rhh20egbzuq3\">@angular/router/testing<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/testing#angularroutertesting\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n  <label class=\"api-type-label NaN\">entry-point</label>\n  \n  \n  \n</header>\n\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\"><p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7ertxi7xq16pwya5507hpwqvu\">為 Angular \n<code><a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a></code> 子系統提供測試模組。</p>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<h2 id=\"entry-point-exports\">入口點的匯出<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/testing#entry-point-exports\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/testing#\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"ngmodules\">NgModules<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/testing#ngmodules\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor deprecated-api-item\"><a href=\"api/router/testing/RouterTestingModule\" class=\"deprecated-api-item\">RouterTestingModule</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          <p><strong>已棄用:</strong> Use <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code> or <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterModule</a></code>/<code>RouterModule.forRoot</code> instead.\nThis module was previously used to provide a helpful collection of test fakes,\nmost notably those for <code><a href=\"api/common/Location\" class=\"code-anchor\">Location</a></code> and <code><a href=\"api/common/LocationStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">LocationStrategy</a></code>.  These are generally not\nrequired anymore, as <code><a href=\"api/common/testing/MockPlatformLocation\" class=\"code-anchor\">MockPlatformLocation</a></code> is provided in <code><a href=\"api/core/testing/TestBed\" class=\"code-anchor\">TestBed</a></code> by default.\nHowever, you can use them directly with <code><a href=\"api/common/testing/provideLocationMocks\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideLocationMocks</a></code>.</p>\n\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f3a9nf9kk68a4n6bvepqll0qt\">設定要用於測試的路由器。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"類\">類<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/testing#類\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"classes\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dtpuzegyjmcbul5yz5jn1ham3\">類<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/testing#classes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/router/testing/RouterTestingHarness\">RouterTestingHarness</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4ktn7ul3f6n9yamevw675744k\">用於 <code><a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a></code> 的測試工具，用於減少測試路由和路由元件所需的樣板檔案。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/router\n - api/router/testing/RouterTestingHarness\n - api/router/testing/RouterTestingModule\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common/Location\n - api/common/LocationStrategy\n - api/common/testing/MockPlatformLocation\n - api/common/testing/provideLocationMocks\n - api/core/testing/TestBed\n - api/router\n - api/router/Router\n - api/router/RouterModule\n - api/router/provideRouter\n - api/router/testing#\n - api/router/testing#angularroutertesting\n - api/router/testing#classes\n - api/router/testing#entry-point-exports\n - api/router/testing#ngmodules\n - api/router/testing#類\n - api/router/testing/RouterTestingHarness\n - api/router/testing/RouterTestingModule\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/router/testing/PACKAGE.md\n-->"